Title: The Tok'ra (1)
Plot: SG-1 locates the Tok'ra, a Goa'uld resistence movement who oppose the System Lords, and attempt to form an alliance. Jacob Carter's cancer brings him near death.
GuestStars: Sarah Douglas, Winston Rekert, Steve Makaj, Tosca Baggoo, Stephen Tibbetts, Roger Haskett, Laara Sadiq, Joy Coghill, Carmen Argenziano
